    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (tmp / wp.sin(0.01))
    v1 = (wp.cos((tmp + 0.96 + v0 + 0.10)) + v1)
    v1 = (wp.cos((v0 + 0.32 / tmp + 0.55)) - v0)
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.exp((v1 + 0.95 * v1 + 0.91)))
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.abs(wp.cos(v2 + 0.79)))
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.cos((tmp + 0.17 - tmp + 0.52)))
    tmp = (wp.cos((v2 + 0.25 + v2 + 1.00)) + wp.cos(wp.abs(v1 + 0.33)))
    data[tid] = v0
